  "meta": {
    "schema_version": "4.0",
    "created_at": "2026-03-19T00:00:00.000Z",
    "notes": "MOMENTUM SCALPER. Three-signal entry system: (1) spot_change_pct > 0.4% + PCR < 1.1 + no fresh CE OI buildup (pure buy momentum, not a hedged move). ELSE: same for down. (2) Buys 0.48 delta — very close to ATM for maximum delta exposure during the move. (3) PYRAMID RULE: if first trade goes +25% and spot still running, opens a SECOND smaller lot at 0.40 delta (slightly OTM) to ride the extended move. (4) STALL RULE: if after 15 minutes spot is flat (±0.2%), close position — momentum is dead, theta killing us. (5) PARTIAL EXIT at 25% P&L on any leg — locks in half position so the rest rides free. (6) max_reentries: 3 — scalper can fire 3 times per day with 45-min cooldown between entries. (7) allow_reentry after SL: true — if stopped out, strategy can enter again on a fresh signal (subject to max 3 total). AVOID on: low VIX slow-chop days, options near expiry (excessive gamma), budget day opening 30 min (too fast, spreads widen)."
  },
